txt.en: Defeated many armoured sentries in Minas Morgul.
You defeated many armoured sentries upon the Circle of Sorrow. The Rangers of Ithilien will be pleased with your efforts.

Armoured sentries keep watch over the Circle of Sorrow. They obey commands from those who control the Circle of Sorrow. Defeating these sentries will allow the Rangers of Ithilien to move about the city with fewer worries.
Armoured sentries can be found in the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should defeat any armoured sentries that you find.
Armoured sentries under the command of those who control the Dead patrol the Circle of Sorrow.
